# Suka Smart Assistant — Inventory System Scratch Plan
# (Storehouse + Kitchen + Root Cellar + Animals/Butchery + Animal Shares/Orders LINKED TO CUT SHEETS)
# Style: BLUF + actionable checklists + event hooks

0) BLUF
- Build an intuitive Inventory core that:
  • Tracks food, supplies, tools, animals, processed packages, and **reserved buyer shares** across locations:
    Pantry, Freezer, Fridge, Root Cellar, Garden Shed, Storehouse A/B, “In-Transit”, “Chill Room”, **“Reserved/<BuyerId>”**.
  • Syncs with: Meals (Recipe Vault, Batch Cooking), Garden (Harvest → produce[]), Preservation trackers, **Animals & Butchery** (intake → slaughter → cut sheet → packaging → labels), and **Animal Share Sales**.
  • **Sales are tightly bound to specific animals & cut sheets**: allocation must use packages created from the linked animal(s) and cut sheet(s) unless an admin enables pooling.
  • Supports barcode/QR, unit conversions, FEFO/FIFO, low-stock alerts with “make at home” or buy recommendations.
  • UI: horizontal “raised card” layout: Overview | Receive/Scan | Use/Decrement | Locations Map | Preservation | **Animals/Butchery** | **Animal Shares/Orders (Cut-Sheet Linked)** | Lists & Purchasing | Analytics/Savings.
  • Emits automation events for calendar, shopping, garden, meals, animals, **sales**, supply lines/logistics.

1) One-liners (Job → Output → Next Best Action → Events)
• Receive: “Scan/enter items → receipt batch + labels → ‘Commit’ → inventory.received”
• Use: “Recipe/Batch consumes → delta preview → ‘Apply/Undo’ → inventory.updated”
• Garden: “Log harvest → produce[] + location → ‘Move to root cellar’ → harvest.logged”
• Preservation: “Select method → derived SKUs + labels → ‘Log preservation’ → preservation.logged”
• **Animals Intake**: “Register animal(s) → intake record + feeding plan → ‘Schedule processing’ → animals.registered”
• **Butchery**: “Upload/Fill cut sheet → package SKUs + yield calc + labels → ‘Commit to inventory’ → butchery.completed”
• **Animal Shares (Linked)**: “Offer quarter/half/whole/bulk with AN-IDs/CS-IDs → reservations + invoices → ‘Finalize allocation (enforce linkage)’ → sales.order.finalized”
• Pickup/Delivery: “Schedule buyer pickup (Hebrew guard) → packing slips + signatures → ‘Complete handoff’ → sales.order.fulfilled”
• Lists: “Low stock & plan delta → unified Shopping/Grocery list → ‘Send to mobile/print’ → lists.generated”
• Audit: “Cycle count by zone → discrepancies report → ‘Reconcile’ → inventory.reconciled”
• Alerts: “Expiry/low stock → notifications + make/buy suggestions → ‘Acknowledge’ → inventory.alert.acknowledged”

