5) UI Acceptance Criteria
☐ “Receive” fast; suggested locations; labels print.
☐ “Use” shows FEFO picks; Apply/Undo cleanly.
☐ LocationMap drag-drop works; emits move events.
☐ Preservation creates derived SKUs & labels; logs method/dates.
☐ **Animals & Butchery** produces correct packages, yields, labels, location moves; cooling compliance tracked.
☐ **Animal Shares (Linked)**: offers can’t be created without Animal IDs; allocation shows only eligible packages; cross-animal blocked unless pooling.
☐ Unified List grouped by store aisle; export PDF/SMS/email.
☐ Analytics shows savings, velocity, turnover, **live→carcass→retail yields**, spoilage, **revenue by animal**.
☐ Hebrew/Sabbath guard for slaughter/packaging/pickups.

6) Domain Preferences & Constraints
- Hebrew calendar & Sabbath: shift processing & pickups off feast days; propose prep-day alternatives.
- Torah constraints: species handling; avoid mixing with non-kosher; separate tooling if required.
- Preservation compliance: low-acid warnings; label method/date; safe-handling for raw meats.
- Butchery safety: chill windows (e.g., ≤4°C/40°F quickly); logs for audit.
- Units: base units per SKU; package weights (lb/kg) & counts (ct); grind % and trim captured.
- Rotation: FEFO default; FIFO fallback.
- Sales policy: deposits, substitution tolerances (±%), refunds on shortfall, buyer consent required to enable pooling.

7) Event Contract (emit/subscribe)
Emit:
  • inventory.received ({batchId, items})
  • inventory.updated ({patchId, delta})
  • inventory.moved ({sku, from, to, qty})
  • inventory.alert.lowstock ({sku, qty, par})
  • inventory.alert.expiring ({sku, lot, expiresOn})
  • lists.generated ({listId, channel})
  • preservation.logged ({method, items, ts})
  • savings.updated ({amount, period})

  • animals.registered ({animalIds, intake})
  • animals.processing.scheduled ({events})
  • animals.processing.started|completed ({runId})

  • butchery.cut_sheet.created ({sheetId})
  • butchery.carcass.chilled ({animalId, tempLog})
  • butchery.packaging.run.started|completed ({runId})
  • **butchery.completed ({animalId, cutSheetId, packages, yields})**

  • **sales.offer.opened ({offerId, animalIds, cutSheetIds})**
  • **sales.order.reserved ({orderId, buyer})**
  • **sales.order.invoiced ({orderId, invoiceId, amount})**
  • **sales.payment.recorded ({orderId, amount, method})**
  • **sales.order.allocated ({orderId, packages, animalIds, cutSheetIds})**
  • **sales.order.finalized ({orderId, deltaMove, animalIds, cutSheetIds})**
  • **sales.pickup.scheduled ({orderId, event})**
  • **sales.order.fulfilled ({orderId, ts})**

Subscribe:
  • recipes.consolidated → computeDeltaFromRecipes
  • batch.started|completed → proposeMakeOrBuy; update use forecast
  • harvest.logged → add produce[] & location prompt
  • **animals.registered|processing.scheduled → block conflicting calendar windows**
  • **butchery.cut_sheet.created → open mapper & packaging run**
  • **butchery.completed → refresh eligible packages for linked offers**
  • calendar.updated/hebrewCalendar.updated → shift shopping/processing/pickup events
  • user.prefs.updated → recalc make/buy, pricing defaults, label format

